# 4. Function to Check Even or Odd

## Problem

Check whether number is even or odd.

## Solution

```python
def check(num):

    if num % 2 == 0:
        return "Even"

    else:
        return "Odd"

print(check(7))
```

## Output

```text
Odd
```

